headline: The Trade Desk (TTD) Shares Skyrocket, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of digital advertising platform The Trade Desk (NASDAQ:TTD) jumped 6.6% in the afternoon session after the company announced plans to launch "Audience Unlimited," a new AI-powered platform designed to overhaul its digital advertising data marketplace.

headline: The Trade Desk Announces Major Overhaul of Digital Advertising Data Marketplace
summary: VENTURA, Calif., September 29, 2025--The Trade Desk (NASDAQ: TTD) today announced plans to launch Audience Unlimited – a major upgrade to the marketplace for third-party data within digital advertising.
